LYON E-SPORT TAKES A NEW DIMENSION FOR ITS 2018 EDITION

WEDNESDAY 25 OCTOBER 2017

   The time has come to announce the come back of the Lyon e-Sport in its
   2018 version. A larger place, more animations, more cashprize and a new
   exhibition zone !

A new place for the Lyon e-Sport 2018

   We want to continuously improve our events, and that is why we decided
   to add new elements for this Lyon e-Sport 2018. To do so, we decided to
   relocate! The Lyon e-Sport 2018 will take place in a new venue, fitting
   our new ambitions, your expectations and the development of esport.

   This is why we are waiting for you on the 16, 17 and 18 of February at
   the Lyon Convention Center ("Cité des Congrès" in French) ! This huge
   place will make us able to produce an even greater and more qualitative
   show than we did previously. We will be able to host much more people
   than the previous years. Moreover, this new place gives us the
   possibility to set up a lot of novelties in order to turn the event
   into a real esport festival.


On the tournament side: Better conditions and higher cashprize

   As usual, the event will host a League of legends tournament open to
   both amateur and professional teams. Last year, 64 teams competed and
   Gamers Origins found the path to victory in a week-end full of
   surprises.

   This new place will allow us to offer more space to players. Thanks to
   it, they will be able to play in an even more comfortable environment,
   allowing them to focus on being the best possible ingame. Our internet
   network get some upgrades as well, with a 2Gb symmetrical broadband and
   one IP per player, in order to offer the best conditions for both
   players and streamers.

   The League of Legends tournament will keep its usual format. After a
   group stage involving every teams, they will be spread into 3 different
   tournaments: Pro, Elite and Amateur according to their results. This
   format guarantees both a chance to try your luck versus the best teams,
   as well as not being directly eliminated, giving you the chance to play
   competitive matches with something to win until the end of the
   week-end, regardless of your level.

   Finally, in order to increase the stakes and to reward players even
   more, the Lyon e-Sport 2018 will come with a higher cashprize. The Pro
   tournament will be rewarded with a 25 000€ cashprize (5 000€ more than
   last year) and we now add 5 000€ for the Elite tournament. The Amateur
   one will be rewarded with numerous gifts other than money.

   We hope all of the above will multiply the motivation of players to
   give their best! Let’s note as well that it is not impossible to see
   some additional surprises on the tournament side this year…


On the spectator side: A new exhibition area and animations

   Main and major novelty this year: we open a great exhibition area!
   Thanks to it, in addition with the show and broadcasted matches on
   stage, you will have the opportunity to enjoy many and various
   animations in this new area. It will be a chance to meet your favorite
   streamers/youtubers, and to play games! To make a long story short: you
   will have no time to be bored! We will disclose our different stands
   and animations progressively, so stay tuned!

   The Lyon e-Sport take a new dimension this year and we hope all these
   novelties will please you. We count on you from the 16 to the 18 of
   February at the Lyon Convention Center for the Lyon e-Sport 2018! While
   waiting for that, note in your schedule that the ticketing will open on
   December 15th for both players and spectators. Do not hesitate to
   follow us on social networks to have all news about the Lyon e-Sport
   2018.

